{
  "message": "fix(tests): add missing CompatRuntime import to 6 integration test files\n\nThe run_async_test helper calls runtime.block_on() which requires the\nCompatRuntime trait to be in scope. 6 files were missing this import,\ncausing E0599 compile errors.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
